lead_paragraph: Nigia Greene scored 14 points and Laura Cornelius added 13 to lead four players in double figures, and No. 14 Miami beat Loyola of Chicago 81-43 on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: No. 14 Miami Women Beat Winless Loyola of Chicago 81-43
